  "figureCaption": "Figure 1. Quantitative gap map between the analytic Melnikov homoclinic-tangle threshold A_c(gamma) and the measured period-doubling onset A_PD(gamma) of the primary period-1 attractor at omega=2/3. Error bars report the onset-localization contract, the dashed line marks A_PD/A_c=1, and the vertical marker is the interpolated reversal where the cascade begins below the first-order Melnikov prediction.",
